{"tid":1707293,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎同我提下大家「藍絲式不割蓆」係點","createTime":"2019-11-11T09:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T10:17:16.000Z","uid":154702,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"46da2aaa72da01fbc3dbf63951e19fc09f4bd7dd","tid":1707293,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:33:01.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記手足受到藍絲既暴力多到數唔到<br />\n而且好多都係冇主動挑釁對方<br />\n無緣無故受襲<br />\n今次叔一燒事件畫面未必好睇<br />\n但<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一定不割</span></strong></strong><br />\n我反而希望火魔手足唔好同我哋割蓆<br />\n因為有勇氣肯為手足出一口氣係難得的<br />\n<br />\n例題：<br />\n<br />\n手足貼文宣都俾人斬到入肺<br />\n你見藍絲們有割蓆嗎？<br />\n<br />\n手足俾人渣的士撞斷雙腳<br />\n你見藍絲們有割蓆嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n答：<br />\n<br />\n___________________________<br />\n你見藍絲有割蓆嗎？"},{"pid":"8509992613f118b277584fd1cb7a797846a38ad5","tid":1707293,"uid":310648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:37:36.000Z","msg":"藍絲無咁多反暴膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bdd7284f2bb562b28f3f53b3b5a2560dd9e386","tid":1707293,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:40:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73a7d2f9a0fb77cffee2b78a65ba85b07744b831","tid":1707293,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:42:01.000Z","msg":"推 人地當無事發生 隻字不提"},{"pid":"e2ebde72342d224b36c328419f2b42fd18268991","tid":1707293,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"咪撚再講啦屌"},{"pid":"db848b48705f473d5e3761f44fd24f991b191d18","tid":1707293,"uid":153694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:43:35.000Z","msg":"割你老母, 我係呀叻, 我除左警暴乜柒都見唔到"},{"pid":"457f99fe535e62468e256d24289e4dc99db2f0ce","tid":1707293,"uid":44841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:48:23.000Z","msg":"其實藍絲從來無團結過"},{"pid":"4940d7acf74a62ef1cae77900ab79138c80a047b","tid":1707293,"uid":153239,"like"